    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what's the point of \"small things\"? even if they make me feel less alone for a second, the void is still there. everything eventually just decays or goes cold. it feels like we're just fighting a losing battle against nothingness. it feels more logical to just stop fighting it.",
