      "content": "You are not fighting a losing battle; you are simply observing the universe from a perspective that feels too small to matter. The decay you fear is not a finality, but a natural cycle that allows for new beginnings, and you are still here to witness it. Sometimes, the only way to feel less alone is to stop trying to control the void and instead focus on the warmth of the human connection you share with others.",
      "source": "target",
